        "\n",
        "As with any contentious issue, when it comes to food, people have differing points of view. [@ERIKSSON2023229] discusses best practices for reducing food waste in Sweden and [@ROOS2023107623] identified 5 perspectives in a small study (n = 106) of views on the Swedish food system.\n",
