        "Double Eleven 11/11 celebrated on November 11 is the world's largest shopping festival [@double11festival2023]. In June 2023, 526 million people watch e-commerce live-streams in China; online bargaining is a type of ritual [@liuBargainingChineseLivestream2024]. According to [@iginiEnvironmentalImpactOnline2024] *\"Asia is set to account for 50% of the world's total online retail sales\"*. [@theinfluencerfactoryStatusSocialCommerce2021] China is the furthest ahead in *social shopping*, the Chinese and U.S. market may be mature and growth will come from emerging markets (SEA, Latin-America)."
