    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Meanwhile the cumulative CO~2e~ emissions trend in the UK in the same time-frame show the historic responsibility of UK [@globalcarbonbudgetCumulativeCOEmissions2023].\n",
        "\n",
        "CO~2~e emissions and GDP growth per capita follow a similar path in the BRICS countries (Brazil, Russia, India, China, South Africa) as well as in Vietnam and Somalia [@vianaespinosadeoliveiraRenewableNonrenewableEnergy2022; @warsameNaturalDisastersDeforestation2024; @raihanSustainabilityVietnamExamining2024]."
