        "|---------------------------|-------------------|---------------------------|\n",
        "| Climate damage per 1 °C warming (China) | ≈ 1.5 % of China’s GDP | Average estimate across FUND, RICE and PAGE |\n",
        "| Climate damage per 1 °C warming (global) | ≈ 0.7 % of world GDP | Average estimate across FUND, RICE and PAGE |\n",
