        "There are many standards. [@internationaltradecentreStandardsMap2022] currently lists 334 different sustainability standards: \"Towards a meaningful economy\" \"The world's largest database for sustainability standards\", \"We provide free, accessible, comprehensive, verified and transparent information on over 300 standards for environmental protection, worker and labor rights, economic development, quality and food safety, as well as business ethics.\"\n",
